  <description><![CDATA[<p>Art Deco Hotel Montana is on the hillside above <a data-udi="umb://document/56819e7662924ccf91baa56999b5cbef" href="/{localLink:umb://document/56819e7662924ccf91baa56999b5cbef}" title="Lucerne">Lucerne</a>'s beautiful old town, with panoramic views over the rooftops to the lake and the mountains beyond. The hotel has a private lift from its elevated position down onto the street, giving easy access to the city and the waterfront and making exploring easy if you can prise yourself away from this beautiful city retreat.</p>
<h2>Room with a view</h2>
<p>Hotel Montana has received the TripAdvisor's Traveller's Choice Award, a testament to their dedication to quality and guest satisfaction. You'll get a good night's sleep in the bright and airy rooms which are comfortable and stylishly designed. Opt for one looking out over the lake to get the best of the spectacular views.</p>
<h2>Fine food and wine</h2>
<p>Tuck into delicious meals in the hotel's award-winning Scala Restaurant, which boasts beautiful views over the city and lake. Enjoy lazy afternoons by the water - kick back and relax at the Beach Club terrace. As the day turns to night, settle down with a drink in the elegant Louis' Bar or the cosy Hemingway Lounge.</p>]]></description>
