  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Hillside Twin/Double Rooms</strong> are around 22-26m² and sleep two people with either twin or double beds (please let us know your preference at the time of booking). These rooms are north-facing with hillside view.</p>
<p><strong>Lake View Twin/Double Rooms</strong> are around 22-26m² and have a balcony and lake view.</p>
<p><strong>Hillside Single Rooms</strong> are around 17-20m² and have a queen bed. These rooms north-facing with hillside view.</p>
<p><strong>Lake View Single Rooms</strong> are around 13-20m² and have a balcony and lake view.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Air conditioning</li>
<li>Tea &amp; coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Bath or shower</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>General information</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Check-in: <strong>3pm</strong></li>
<li>Check-out: <strong>12pm</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes</strong></p>
<p>A resort tourist tax of approx. CHF 4.40 per person per night is payable locally. Children aged 11 and under are exempt.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Steps into property: <strong>No</strong></li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
